data.description:
Tired of hearing...."Honey, nice house but the kitchen and bathrooms are really dated". You won't hear that on this home.
This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home has a completely remodeled kitchen and bathrooms. A 500 sq. ft. great room has been added on the back. The home measures just under 2,000 sq. ft. This brick home features a large fenced back yard, immaculate landscaping and is neat as a pin. The new owner will need no extra money for remodeling. The great room with its many large windows and large fireplace, opens widely to the dining room and kitchen. House is located on a quiet boulevard in a nice neighborhood on the north end of town.
data.whatILove: The Kitchen and family room are open and remodeled......family room has a neat bar are not to mention the many updates throughout this home .......landscape is new and beautiful.....roof ac and furnace  replaced within the last 5 years
